library(dslabs) data(polls_us_election_2016)
print(head(polls_us_election_2016, 10)) print(sum(is.na(polls_us_election_2016)))
polls_us_election_2016_new <- polls_us_election_2016
birth_year <- 2001
first_name <- “Atacan”
for (i in 1:length(polls_us_election_2016_new)) {
if (is.numeric(polls_us_election_2016_new[[i]])) { polls_us_election_2016_new[[i]][is.na(polls_us_election_2016_new[[i]])] <- birth_year } else if (is.character(polls_us_election_2016_new[[i]])) { polls_us_election_2016_new[[i]][is.na(polls_us_election_2016_new[[i]])] <- first_name } }
print(head(polls_us_election_2016_new, 10)) remaining_na <- sum(is.na(polls_us_election_2016_new))
cat(“Yeni veri cercevesindeki kalan NA sayisi:”, remaining_na, “”)
